{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0002", "text": "泡麪跟我是朋友 熟悉得不須要抬頭", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 2, 3, 5, 2, 0, 5, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["paau1", "min6", "gan1", "ngo5", "si6", "pang4", "jau5", "suk6", "sik1", "dak1", "bat1", "seoi1", "jiu3", "toi4", "tau4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "泡麪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "朋友", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "熟悉", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "須要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抬頭", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "獨男", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4946", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0003", "text": "不管我 留嘴邊的污垢", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 5, 0, 9, 3, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "gun2", "ngo5", "lau4", "zeoi2", "bin1", "dik1", "wu1", "gau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不管", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "留", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嘴邊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "污垢", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "獨男", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4946", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0004", "text": "不知我 連番激鬥沒對手才獨鬥", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 5, 0, 3, 3, 4, 2, 4, 9, 0, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "zi1", "ngo5", "lin4", "faan1", "gik1", "dau3", "mut6", "deoi3", "sau2", "coi4", "duk6", "dau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "連番", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "激鬥", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "獨鬥", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "獨男", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4946", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0005", "text": "殺光種種妖獸 但我也快要成爲怪獸", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 3, 9, 9, 3, 4, 2, 5, 5, 4, 4, 0, 4, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["saat3", "gwong1", "zung2", "zung2", "jiu1", "sau3", "daan6", "ngo5", "jaa5", "faai3", "jiu3", "sing4", "gwaai3", "sau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "殺光", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "種種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "妖獸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "成爲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怪獸", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "獨男", "artists": ["古巨基"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_4946", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_NDk0Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
